# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# EasyMO Admin App - Cloudflare Pages Environment Variables Template
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# This file documents all environment variables required for Cloudflare Pages
# deployment of the EasyMO Admin Panel.
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Go to Cloudflare Dashboard > Pages > easymo-admin > Settings > Environment variables
# 2. Add each variable listed below with appropriate values
# 3. Set Production and Preview environment values as needed
#
# SECURITY NOTES:
# - Never commit actual values to version control
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are exposed to the client browser
# - Never put sensitive keys in NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables
# - Use Cloudflare's encrypted secrets for sensitive values
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BUILD CONFIGURATION
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Node.js version (required)
NODE_VERSION=20.18.0

# Enable Cloudflare Pages identification
CF_PAGES=1

# Disable Next.js telemetry
NEXT_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SUPABASE CONFIGURATION (PUBLIC - Safe for client)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Supabase Project URL (required)
# Format: https://[project-ref].supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co

# Supabase Anonymous Key (required)
# This is the public anon key, safe for client-side use
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# APPLICATION CONFIGURATION (PUBLIC - Safe for client)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Environment label displayed in the admin panel
# Values: production, staging, preview, development
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENVIRONMENT=production

# Environment label for UI display
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENVIRONMENT_LABEL=Production

# Mock data toggle (must be 'false' in production)
NEXT_PUBLIC_USE_MOCKS=false

# UI version toggle
NEXT_PUBLIC_UI_V2_ENABLED=true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI CONFIGURATION (PUBLIC - Safe for client)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Enable/disable AI features
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_AI=true

# AI provider selection (openai, gemini, or both)
NEXT_PUBLIC_AI_PROVIDER=openai

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SERVER-SIDE SECRETS (Add in Cloudflare Dashboard only - never commit!)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These should be added as encrypted environment variables in Cloudflare Pages:
#
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY - Server-side Supabase access (NEVER expose publicly!)
# OPENAI_API_KEY - OpenAI API key for AI features
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY - Google Gemini API key
# ADMIN_SESSION_SECRET - Session encryption key (min 32 characters)
# EASYMO_ADMIN_TOKEN - Admin API authentication token
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CLOUDFLARE PAGES SPECIFIC SETTINGS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Build Command (set in Cloudflare Dashboard):
#   cd .. && pnpm --filter @va/shared build && pnpm --filter @easymo/commons build && pnpm --filter @easymo/video-agent-schema build && pnpm --filter @easymo/ui build && cd admin-app && npm run build
#
# Build Output Directory:
#   .next
#
# Root Directory:
#   admin-app
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Before deploying, verify:
# [ ] NEXT_PUBLIC_USE_MOCKS is set to 'false'
# [ ] NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL points to correct project
# [ ] NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY is the correct anon key
# [ ] All server-side secrets are configured in Cloudflare Dashboard
# [ ] No SERVICE_ROLE or secret keys in NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables
#
